---
import SectionCopy from '../SectionCopy.astro';
---

<section
	class="mt-20 md:mt-24 lg:mt-28 xl:mt-36 relative w-full max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8"
>
	<div class="text-center">
		<span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-blue-purple-gradient font-semibold">
			Pour quoi faire ?
		</span>

		<h2 class="mt-2 font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-white text-balance">
			<strong>Pourquoi HexaGlue</strong>
		</h2>

		<p class="mt-4 text-base text-astro-gray-200 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
			Pour piloter la transformation et fiabiliser l'architecture, à la compilation.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
		<span
			class="px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-full bg-astro-dark-800/50 border border-astro-dark-100/20 text-astro-gray-100"
		>
			Sans contrainte de runtime
		</span>
		<span
			class="px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-full bg-astro-dark-800/50 border border-astro-dark-100/20 text-astro-gray-100"
		>
			Sans framework imposé
		</span>
		<span
			class="px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-full bg-astro-dark-800/50 border border-astro-dark-100/20 text-astro-gray-100"
		>
			Sans lock-in éditeur
		</span>
	</div>
</section>
